    <!--
        Canonical feature definitions — single source of truth for display labels,
        sort order, and feature types used by both the admin billing UI and the
        public pricing / comparison table.

        ALWAYS_ON  – free on every plan (no plan_entitlements row)
        BOOLEAN    – toggled enabled/disabled per plan
        LIMIT      – numeric limit per plan
        PRO_ONLY   – shown as a row but only ticked for the Pro plan
    -->

